SuseGallery Widget

Flavio Castelli
Cristian Messel

The requests we need to do:
  1. Get a list of popular appliances
    curl -u [user]:[key] -X GET "http://susestudio.com/api/v2/gallery/appliances_list/?per_page=1&popular=''"
  2. Get the appliance version
    curl -u [user]:[key] -X GET "http://susestudio.com/api/v2/gallery/appliances/130166"
  3. Start a testdrive of that appliance
    curl -u [user]:[key] -X POST "http://susestudio.com/api/v2/gallery/appliance_testdrive/291415?version=1.0.1"
